messages.message: Hi, is there any guide to make .proto file change? I made some proto change, how to run some command to generate codes?
Let me see if there's a guide, but the command should be `cd webserver/api-server && make build-protos`
Also make sure you run the commit before running `git add`
No need to generate stubs for go code manually. The command above is only used to generate python & JS stubs.
